<br>
The reason there has been no vote yet is no one (myself included) has come up with a legitimate solution.  I can feel the pulse of these boards effectively enough now to know what does and does not stand a chance of being voted favorably upon by the population of the server.  So far, we got nada.<br>
<br>
To wit:<br>
<br>
Basic FCFS -- Won't pass.  Too many people like reservations because they're either casual players or don't enjoy the idea of running around like chickens with their heads cut off trying to organize a full scale raid on the spur of the moment.<br>
<br>
FCFS, two raids -- Won't pass.  Too many people would argue that only one raid should be in there at a time.<br>
<br>
Reservations in the tradition of hate/fear/sky -- Won't pass.  Too many people are sick of reservations.  Too many questions as to how to make a plane with a 30 hour spawn time truly &quot;reservable&quot; and to what extent it should be reservable.  <br>
<br>
Two day reservations -- Won't pass.  Ditto everything said about reservations above, and too many people who feel that two day reservations for a plane this large is overcompensating and wasting potential drops.<br>
<br>
Total FFA -- Won't pass.  Because we're all nice people, at our core, and we WANT to work together.  Yourself included.  Otherwise, you wouldn't bother posting here.<br>
<br>
<br>
I'm not trying to slap you down here...I'm just trying to address your concern about voting on POG. <p><BR>
